						               													<description>Imagine a world where humans never existed.  In its place, several other animal species had the opportunity to evolve and occupy the top of the food chain.  In this world, the future is the present, and the power struggle is even more intense.  Certain species dominate large corporations, while others live forgotten in the underworld.  Welcome to the Persona non Grata universe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In it you take on the mantle of a hacker willing to dismantle this model of tyrannical society.  To do this, you will need to gather information about the corrupt employees of the biggest corporations, sharing them and stealing them from your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game rounds are played simultaneously: You must select an information card, link to one of your action cards (download, send or encrypt) and pass the rest of the information cards in your hand to the next player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After all the information has been played, players compare the relevance of their information in each corporation.  The first two places can score, stealing information cards from other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of 3 rounds, we will count the points.  But be careful, to score in each corporation you will need to activate them with worker cards or headquarters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the artist&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
